    "content": "Every Build follows the same lifecycle.\n\n```text\nDesign Model\n\n↓\n\nValidation\n\n↓\n\nBuild Generation\n\n↓\n\nDeterministic Computation\n\n↓\n\nSnapshot Creation\n\n↓\n\nReview\n\n↓\n\nComparison\n\n↓\n\nApproval\n\n↓\n\nExport\n\n↓\n\nArchive\n```\n\nA Build never returns to the Design Model.\n\nSubsequent work always creates a new Build.\n\n---"
